== 制作 ==

=== 构想与改编 ===
[[File:NorthangerPersuasionTitlePage.jpg|thumb]]

[[简·奥斯汀|简·奥斯汀]]小说改编在20世纪90年代中期突然复兴，发行作品包括《劝导》在内有六部之多<ref name="Parrill-2002">{{cite book | first = Sue | last = Parrill | title = Jane Austen on Film and Television: A Critical Study of the Adaptations | publisher = McFarland | year = 2002 | isbn = 0-7864-1349-2 | url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=l6dsN6KfXUkC&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr | access-date = 2021-07-31 | archive-date = 2014-07-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140726221154/http://books.google.com/books?id=l6dsN6KfXUkC | dead-url = no}}</ref>{{rp|5}}，传媒戏称“奥斯汀狂热”<ref name="Higson-2011">{{cite book | first = Andrew | last = Higson | title = Film England: Culturally English Filmmaking Since the 1990s | publisher = I.B. Tauris | year = 2011 | isbn = 978-1-84885-454-3}}</ref>{{rp|133}}。改编作品热卖往往催生同类新作，但此次“奥斯汀狂热”的不同在于许多项目同时铺开，例如《劝导》就是同电视剧《[[傲慢與偏見_(電視短劇)|傲慢与偏见]]》、电影《[[理性與感性_(電影)|理智与情感]]》同期制作<ref name="Giddings-Selby-2001">{{cite book | first1 = Robert | last1 = Giddings | first2 = Keith | last2 = Selby | title = The Classic Serial on Television and Radio | publisher = Palgrave Macmillan | year = 2001 | isbn = 978-0-312-23598-7}}</ref>{{rp|100}}<ref name="Parrill-2002" />{{rp|6–7}}。电影学者安德鲁·席格森等人认为这纯属巧合，各项目制片人分属不同公司，没有证据表明他们通过任何约定促成如此局面<ref name="Higson-2011" />{{rp|135}}<ref name="Parrill-2002" />{{rp|5–6}}。

英格兰制片人菲奥娜·芬莱多年来一直想把奥斯汀1817年著作《[[勸導_(小說)|劝导]]》改编成电影<ref name="Giddings-Selby-2001" />{{rp|100}}，[[独立电视网|独立电视网]]曾于1971年把小说改编成[[劝导_(1971年电视剧)|同名电视剧]]，[[安·弗班克|安·弗班克]]领衔<ref name="Cardwell-2014">{{cite book | url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=YHWEAwAAQBAJ&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr | last = Cardwell | first = Sarah | editor1-first = Jonathan | editor1-last = Bignell | editor2-first = Stephen | editor2-last = Lacey | title = British Television Drama: Past, Present and Future | publisher = Palgrave Macmillan | year = 2014 | pages = 84–97 | chapter = Persuaded? The Impact of Changing Production Contexts on Three Adaptations of Persuasion | isbn = 978-1-137-32757-4 | access-date = 2021-07-31 | archive-date = 2021-06-22 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210622233015/https://books.google.com/books?id=YHWEAwAAQBAJ}}</ref>{{rp|88}}。芬莱觉得小说情节“非常浪漫”，“大家都能找到共鸣点，失去已久的爱情非常感人”<ref name="Higson-2011" />{{rp|140}}。她对尼克·迪尔在舞台剧领域的建树非常满意，特别是取材[[威廉·贺加斯|威廉·贺加斯]]的剧作《成功艺术》，请他改编奥斯汀的原著<ref name="Dearinterview" />。迪尔起初建议取材奥斯汀的《[[理智与情感|理智与情感]]》或《[[傲慢與偏見|傲慢與偏見]]》，但看过《劝导》后同意改编。在他看来，《劝导》作为奥斯汀最后完成的小说，比其他作品更成熟。<ref name="Giddings-Selby-2001" />{{rp|100}}

迪尔事后表示，《劝说》表面上只是“[[灰姑娘|灰姑娘]]模式爱情故事”，但“立足现实、情感真挚”，特别是讲述两人分离与重聚的情节<ref name="Dear-1996">{{cite book | first = Nick | last = Dear | editor1-first = Nick | editor1-last = Dear | editor2-first = Jane | editor2-last = Austen | chapter = Introduction | title = Persuasion: A Screenplay by Nick Dear | publisher = Methuen Drama | year = 1996 | isbn = 0-413-71170-6}}</ref>。改编过程困难重重，迪尔两年才写出一稿<ref name="Giddings-Selby-2001" />{{rp|100}}。忠于原著的叙事结构、主人翁在上半场几乎没有对白，“所以无法像传统核心人物那样推动剧情”都是他创作期间面临的挑战。迪尔还需努力适应奥斯汀的巧妙措辞，“一切人物特征几乎全靠角色本身传达，字里行间的机智与幽默已超出多数人能力所及。把小说翻译成电影语言非常不易，需要精雕细琢”。<ref name="Dearinterview" />

罗杰·米歇尔的戏剧和电视剧导演经验丰厚，《劝导》是他首次执导电影长片<ref name="BostonGlobe1997">{{Cite news | url = http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-56446016.html | title = Austen takes Root – 'Persuasion' brings rising star to PBS | work = [[波士頓環球報|Boston Globe]] | first = Bart | last = Mills | date = 1997-04-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170701150646/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-56446016.html | dead-url = yes | access-date = 2017-07-01 | archive-date = 2017-07-01}}{{subscription needed}}</ref><ref name="Cardwell-2014" />{{rp|89}}。米歇尔从小就很喜欢奥斯汀的作品，与其他男同学截然不同：“全班男生只有我特别喜欢奥斯汀”。他觉得《劝导》是作者最动人的小说，也是她最接近自传的作品<ref name="wp1">{{cite news | url = http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-865671.html | last = Masters | first = Kim | title = Austen found; Hollywood rediscovers the 19th-century writer | work = [[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]] | date = 1995-12-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160505140643/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-865671.html | dead-url = yes | access-date = 2016-05-05 | archive-date = 2016-05-05}}{{subscription needed}}</ref>。米歇尔认为原著是“充满色欲的情色爱情故事”<ref name="wp1" />，导演本片时注重体现小说中的对比，如“凯林奇庄园冷冰冰的礼节，上层社会的温暖潮湿感”<ref name="Dearinterview" />。皇家海军也是本片创作的关注重点，温特沃斯这类军官复员后的确在财富和经历上超人一等。导演希望通过军官复员后“与过去截然不同的语言和行为习惯”来体现文化交融。<ref name="Dearinterview" />

