主人翁安妮是鲁特出演的第一个院线电影人物<ref name="sfss">{{cite news | last = Sheehan | first = Henry | title = Theater star taking root in first film | work = South Florida Sun-Sentinel | access-date = 2021-07-31 | date = 1995-10-30 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.sun-sentinel.com/news/fl-xpm-1995-10-30-9510270494-story.html | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210702063245/https://www.sun-sentinel.com/news/fl-xpm-1995-10-30-9510270494-story.html | archive-date = 2021-07-02}}</ref>，她宣称“英格兰所有女演员”都曾为出演该角色努力。鲁特曾与导演在1993年电视剧《[[郊区佛爷|郊区佛爷]]》合作，她给米歇尔写信取得试镜机会后通过。<ref name="sfc">{{cite news | last = Stack | first = Peter | title = Art of 'Persuasion' brings Root to U.S. | work = [[旧金山纪事报|San Francisco Chronicle]] | date = 1995-10-11 | access-date = 2021-07-31 | archive-date = 2017-12-31 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171231155500/http://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/Art-of-Persuasion-Brings-Root-to-U-S-English-3021928.php | url = https://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/Art-of-Persuasion-Brings-Root-to-U-S-English-3021928.php}}</ref><ref name="bfibuddha">{{Cite news | url = https://www2.bfi.org.uk/films-tv-people/4ce2b7cfe16a3 | title = The Buddha of Suburbia Part 4 (1993) | publisher = [[英國電影協會|British Film Institute]] | access-date = 2021-07-31 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201029111146/https://www2.bfi.org.uk/films-tv-people/4ce2b7cfe16a3 | archive-date = 2020-10-29}}</ref>。鲁特很想出演安妮这种“难驾驭”的人物，自称喜欢诠释人物“从压抑到快乐绽放的成长历程”<ref name="BostonGlobe1997" />。参与制作的美国波士顿WGBH电视台本想找更出名的演员扮演主人翁，看过鲁特的试镜表现后改变主意<ref name="Giddings-Selby-2001" />{{rp|102}}。

鲁特发现原著的叙事风格足以表达主人翁心理，但改编电影对白很少，“大部分时间必须在不开口的情况下传达一段又一段剧情。我根本没考虑技术问题，只管反复阅读（原著），设法传达其中感受。”<ref name="wwd1995" />本片按剧情时间顺序摄制，方便鲁特了解主人翁“心中不快会造成多大差异”，与片尾心境开阔后人也变美对比有多显著<ref name="sfss" />。在鲁特看来，安妮远比她在[[皇家莎士比亞劇團|皇家莎士比亞劇團]]扮演的[[麦克白夫人|麦克白夫人]]等人物沉默<ref name="wwd1995">{{Cite news | url = http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-17508951.html | title = Straight from the Root | work = [[女裝日報|Women's Wear Daily]] | last = Botton | first = Sari | date = 1995-09-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160307161504/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-17508951.html | dead-url = yes | access-date = 2016-03-07 | archive-date = 2016-03-07}}{{subscription needed}}</ref>。饰演弗雷德里克·温特沃斯的爱尔兰男演员塞伦·希德认为奥斯汀“深知男人心理有时多么脆弱”<ref name="Parrill-2002" />{{rp|155}}。他特别认可温特沃特工作称职，但一遇到安妮就“不善交际”的描写<ref name="Parrill-2002" />{{rp|155}}。诠释拉塞尔夫人的苏珊·弗利特伍德曾与米歇尔在《郊区佛爷》合作<ref name="bfibuddha" /><ref>{{Cite news | dead-url = no | url = https://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/obituary-susan-fleetwood-5646845.html | title = Obituary: Susan Fleetwood | work = [[獨立報|The Independent]] | date = 1995-10-01 | access-date = 2021-07-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160428054201/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/obituary-susan-fleetwood-5646845.html | archive-date = 2016-04-28}}</ref>，她在摄制收工后不久去世，本片是她的遗作<ref>{{cite news | url = https://www2.bfi.org.uk/films-tv-people/4ce2b9f032d0b | title = Susan Fleetwood | publisher = [[英國電影協會|British Film Institute]] | access-date = 2021-07-31 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201203170533/https://www2.bfi.org.uk/films-tv-people/4ce2b9f032d0b | archive-date = 2020-12-03}}</ref>。

=== 化妆与服饰 ===
[[File:Persuasion_1995_film_scene.png|thumb]]

米歇尔力求忠于原著，尤其注重避免他对其他19世纪时代剧非常反感的人工雕琢痕迹。他自称“竭力想把电影拍得好像隔壁人家的故事。我想描绘真实的人，而不是梳妆、发型、地毯”。<ref name="wp1" />导演认为真实表现人物年龄能增强戏剧感，要求演员不要化妆，也不要总收拾得干干净净<ref name="wp1" />。鲁特接受采访时自称“基本没化妆，发型显然很不讨喜……感觉灯光也很刺眼，大家都不好看”<ref name="sfss" />。她还在另一次采访时表示，主人翁平淡无奇但还不至痛苦不堪，在生活中找到自我满足的渠道，只是身边总有人喋喋不休，影响人物情绪<ref name="sfc" />。鲁特认为，真实反映人物年龄是本片重要卖点<ref name="sfc" />。

负责本片服装的亚历山德拉·伯恩着眼令服装“立足现实”<ref>{{Cite news | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | url = https://variety.com/1995/film/reviews/persuasion-1200442005/ | title = Review: 'Persuasion' | work = [[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] | first = Derek | last = Elley | date = 1995-06-06 | access-date = 2021-08-01 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210308192048/https://variety.com/1995/film/reviews/persuasion-1200442005/}}</ref>，看上去“穿过”<ref name="Giddings-Selby-2001" />{{rp|102}}。伯恩也曾投身《郊区佛爷》<ref name="bfibuddha" />，《劝导》是她首次为电影设计古装<ref>{{Cite news | archive-date = 2015-05-01 | url = http://www.latimesmagazine.com/2011/02/rule-britannia.html | title = Rule Britannia! | work = Los Angeles Times Magazine | first = Gina | last = McIntyre | date = 2011-02 | access-date = 2015-05-01 | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150501151915/http://www.latimesmagazine.com/2011/02/rule-britannia.html}}</ref>。本片经常要与同期摄制的[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]电视剧《傲慢与偏见》争夺服饰与道具<ref name="Parrill-2002" />{{rp|6}}，剧组后来只能从意大利和澳大利亚购买替代品<ref name="Giddings-Selby-2001" />{{rp|103}}。伯恩因本片获[[英國電視學院獎|英國電視學院獎]]最佳服装设计奖<ref>{{Cite news | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2021-02-24 | url = http://awards.bafta.org/award/1996/tvcraft/costume-design | title = Television Craft Costume Design in 1996 | publisher = [[英国电影和电视艺术学院|British Academy of Film and Television Arts]] | access-date = 2021-08-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210224070931/http://awards.bafta.org/award/1996/tvcraft/costume-design}}</ref>。

英国电影协会旗下“银幕在线”网站刊登露易丝·沃森的文章，称本片服装与化妆有助于表现主人翁类似灰姑娘的完整转变过程。起初她为家庭牺牲的价值为人忽视，仿佛错过花期的花朵。松松垮垮的服饰暗示回绝温特沃斯后她是多么憔悴……她重拾信心如花朵般绽放，穿着得体、眼神闪亮，形象变得生机勃勃。”<ref name="screenonline">{{Cite news | url = http://www.screenonline.org.uk/film/id/574332/ | title = Persuasion (1995) | publisher = Screenonline | first = Louise | last = Watson | year = 2014 | access-date = 2021-08-01 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210308024738/http://www.screenonline.org.uk/film/id/574332/ | archive-date = 2021-03-08}}</ref>保莱特·理查兹指出，片中沃尔特爵士等“靠不住”的男人都身着华丽服装。现代文化的“真汉子”往往不在乎衣装，所以片中浮华对现代观众而言特别明显。<ref name="Richards-2003">{{cite book | url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=JYkMbaYAKMoC&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr | last = Richards | first = Paulette | editor1-first = Gina | editor1-last = MacDonald | editor2-first = Andrew | editor2-last = MacDonald | title = Jane Austen on Screen | publisher = Cambridge University Press | year = 2003 | pages = 111–126 | chapter = Regency Romance Shadowing in the Visual Motifs of Roger Michell's Persuasion | isbn = 0-521-79325-4 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140723050441/http://books.google.com/books?id=JYkMbaYAKMoC | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-08-01 | archive-date = 2014-07-23}}</ref>{{rp|114}}片中温特沃斯经常穿海军制服，与[[布莱恩·马歇尔|布莱恩·马歇尔]]在1971年版改编电视剧的着装风格对比显著。制服令温特沃斯从众多男角色中脱颖而出，<ref name="Parrill-2002" />{{rp|155}}人物形象既浪漫又孤独<ref name="Richards-2003" />{{rp|114}}。吉娜·麦克唐纳与安德鲁·麦克唐纳看法类似，称赞本片用上层阶级的奢侈时尚对比皇家海军道德品质，准确捕捉奥斯汀的讽刺笔触。与原著其他改编作品不同，片中海军人员经常身穿制服，着重体现人物职业。<ref>{{cite book | url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=GOWlgZ-8YlIC&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr | last1 = MacDonald | first1 = Gina | last2 = MacDonald | first2 = Andrew | editor1-first = Tiffany | editor1-last = Potter | title = Women, Popular Culture, and the Eighteenth Century | publisher = University of Toronto Press | year = 2012 | pages = 276–279 | chapter = Visualizing Empire in Domestic Settings: Designing Persuasion for the Screen | isbn = 978-1-4426-4181-5 | access-date = 2021-08-01 | archive-date = 2021-06-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210622233016/https://books.google.com/books?id=GOWlgZ-8YlIC | dead-url = no}}</ref>

