}}
《劝导》上映早期没有引起多少影评人关注<ref name="Collins-2001" />，但《傲慢与偏见》、《理智与情感》同年在英国大卖后情况生变，奥斯汀人气高涨，促使评论家把目光投向之前发行的电影<ref name="Greenfield-Troost-2001" /><ref name="Collins-2001" />。知名影评人高度评价本片<ref name="Scholz-2013" />{{rp|135}}，评论汇总网站[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]共收集29篇评论，认可度达八成六<ref>{{Cite news | url = https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1066528-persuasion | title = Persuasion (1995) | publisher = [[爛番茄|Rotten Tomatoes]] | access-date = 2021-08-01 | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2021-03-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210318075143/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1066528-persuasion/ }}</ref>。《纽约时报》的卡琳·詹姆斯认为本片堪称“影评人之选”，“演员全面跟进奥斯汀温馨又犀利的风格”<ref name="nytimesreview" />。杰伊·卡尔在《[[波士頓環球報|波士頓環球報]]》发文赞赏鲁特的演出，认为她的电影处女作人物寡言少语，但表现非常出彩，令人“心脏忘记跳动”<ref>{{Cite news | archive-date = 2017-07-05 | url = http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-8346833.html | title = 'Persuasion' convinces | work = [[波士頓環球報|Boston Globe]] | first = Jay | last = Carr | date = 1995-10-06 | access-date = 2017-07-05 | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170705150621/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-8346833.html}}{{subscription needed}}</ref>。

《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》刊登戴森·豪的文章，赞扬影片“美妙而从容的精致，任何关注电影制作的人都知道，体现奥斯汀的才华需要投入时间和耐心。”在他看来，本片表演可靠，方向把握精准，剧本巧妙而灿烂，堪称灵感四射。<ref>{{Cite news | url = http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-860986.html | title = 'Persuasion': Worth waiting for | work = The Washington Post | first = Desson | last = Howe | date = 1995-10-20 | access-date = 2016-10-18 | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161018230327/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-860986.html | archive-date = 2016-10-18}}{{subscription needed}}</ref>。[[肯·塔克|肯·塔克]]在《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》为本片打分“A–”（最高A+），声称没看过原著的观众也会对本片着迷<ref name="ewreview" />。他赞扬《劝导》激情四射、把握精准，足以提醒观众奥斯汀为何至今仍是如此大家<ref name="ewreview">{{Cite news | archive-date = 2021-03-09 | url = https://ew.com/article/1995/10/06/persuasion/ | title = Persuasion | work = [[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] | last = Tucker | first = Ken | date = 1995-10-06 | access-date = 2021-08-01 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210309030929/https://ew.com/article/1995/10/06/persuasion/}}</ref>。19世纪文学教授苏珊·奥斯特罗夫·魏瑟称本片“忠实演绎奥斯汀的世界”，鲁特扮演的安妮非常聪慧，对人物的懊悔与失意表达准确、巧妙，堪称影片“皇冠上的珠宝”<ref>{{cite book | first = Susan | last = Ostrov Weisser | chapter = Inspired by Persuasion | editor-first1 = Jane | editor-last1 = Austen | editor-link1 = 简·奥斯汀 | editor-first2 = Susan | editor-last2 = Ostrov Weisser | title = Persuasion | publisher = Fine Creative Media | year = 2003 | orig-year = 1817 | isbn = 978-1-59308-130-0 | page = 241}}</ref>。2008年，詹姆斯·兰普顿在《[[獨立報|獨立報]]》发文，把本片排在史上所有奥斯汀改编作品第四位<ref>{{Cite news | dead-url = yes | url = https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/bonnets-and-bustles-the-best-austen-adaptations-5325185.html | title = Bonnets and bustles: The best Austen adaptations | work = The Independent | last = Rampton | first = James | date = 2008-07-24 | access-date = 2021-08-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110812050100/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/senseless-sensibility-just-another-jane-austen-adaptation-875661.html | archive-date = 2011-08-12}}</ref>。

影评人把本片和《理智与情感》对比，后者在好莱坞赢得的[[理智与情感获奖名单|荣誉]]和认可更多<ref name="Parrill-2002" />{{rp|201}}，[[奢侈品|高端市场]]评论家称赞《劝导》更真实体贴地再现奥斯汀世界<ref name="Higson-2011" />{{rp|140, 158}}。《纽约时报》的[[珍妮特·马斯林|珍妮特·马斯林]]认为，本片的巧妙与精辟更有说服力，是设想最周到的奥斯汀改编作品，《理智与情感》无法相比<ref>{{Cite news | archive-date = 2021-07-03 | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1995/12/13/movies/film-review-in-mannerly-search-of-marriageable-men.html | title = Film review; In mannerly search of marriageable men | work = The New York Times | first = Janet | last = Maslin | date = 1995-12-13 | access-date = 2021-08-01 | dead-url = no | page = C15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210703045401/https://www.nytimes.com/1995/12/13/movies/film-review-in-mannerly-search-of-marriageable-men.html}}</ref>。《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》称《劝导》“最真实的英国版，也是最接近小说精髓的版本”，《理智与情感》则是“奥斯汀最讨好观众的好莱坞版，表现温和、以取悦观众为目标”<ref>{{Cite news | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1995-12-13-ca-13370-story.html | title = Movie Review: An Austen-tatious Year : ‘Sensibility’ Is the Most Audience-Friendly of Recent Adaptations | work = [[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]] | first = Kenneth | last = Turan | date = 1995-12-13 | access-date = 2021-08-01 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210308083110/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1995-12-13-ca-13370-story.html | archive-date = 2021-03-08}}</ref>。《[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]》认为两部电影都是1995年的杰作，其中《劝导》更含蓄，《理智与情感》更热闹<ref>{{Cite news | url = http://content.time.com/time/subscriber/article/0,33009,983896,00.html | title = The best of 1995: Cinema | work = [[時代雜誌|Time]] | date = 1995-12-25 | access-date = 2021-08-01 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200218111146/http://content.time.com/time/subscriber/article/0,33009,983896,00.html | archive-date = 2020-02-18}}</ref>。席格森分析两部电影时指出，《劝导》对现实感把握精准、坚韧，对《[[曼斯菲尔德庄园_(1999年电影)|曼斯菲尔德庄园]]》（1999年）、《[[珍奧斯汀少女日記|珍奧斯汀少女日記]]》（2007年）等奥斯汀改编作品影响很大<ref name="Higson-2011" />{{rp|143}}。

